Patrick M. Prevost 
Executive Compensation
As Former President and CEO, Director at CABOT CORP, Patrick M. Prevost  made $12,335,109 in total compensation.  Of this total $835,546 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $2,739,358 was received in stock options, $7,059,331 was awarded as stock and $1,700,874 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


